{"tid":1187624,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"自慰既高潮讓我了解到咩係眾生皆平等","createTime":"2019-06-05T19:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T05:34:23.000Z","uid":257341,"like":49,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1596aa24edbe43bd953fd0fa6912e42fc7a07831","tid":1187624,"uid":257341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T19:14:03.000Z","msg":"話說我有一個做interior design，ok出名既ex。<br />\n我一直都好撚憎佢。<br />\n佢玩鳩過我幾次，同完我分手幾個月之後又搵番我，但一齊唔夠一個禮拜又比佢飛多次。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分手之後個幾年，條仆街就越黎越紅，好多客搵佢做野又雜誌訪問又盛。<br />\n雖然佢又肥又樣衰，但因為佢紅，所以越黎越多女埋佢身。<br />\n而我，就普普通通打份工。<br />\n幾年過去，其實我心裡面仲會暗暗地同佢比較。<br />\n最近我以為我已經move on左，但頭先屎忽痕睇佢IG，<br />\n點知<br />\n佢同咗個 女 神 級 model 鬼 妹 一 齊！！！！！！！！<br />\n仲要係金髮大波，一定係pink lin個隻！！！！<br />\n睇完之後 我繼續扮無野同老豆響廳睇夜晚重播個套法證先鋒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但同時腦海就不停浮現條仆街屌鬼妹既畫面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好難受，因為一直想佢仆街點知佢宜家真係乜都有啦！！！<br />\n我入番房，坐左響床，諗左陣，<br />\n覺得與其沉溺過去，不如諗辦法令自己開心。<br />\n於是我打開櫃桶，拎咗個枝成千蚊買番泥，made in Germany既自慰棒出黎，<br />\n跟手響Spotify揀左個有格調既coffeehouse playlist，<br />\n然後張開雙腿，<br />\n慢慢按摩陰蒂。<br />\n隨著我身體慢慢放鬆，<br />\n我將自慰棒既強度逐漸加大，<br />\n然後一浪接一浪既高潮迎面而來，<br />\n啊～我是感到如此自主和如此自由。<br />\n依一刻我感受到，<br />\n無論你pink lin又好，brown lin又好，<br />\n高潮就係高潮，無年齡，職業，國籍之分，<br />\n正所謂 we are the world we are the children！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依一刻，我決定將一切怒恨都讓分泌沖走，<br />\n好好同我枝自慰棒生活落去。<br />\n各位晚安。"},{"pid":"84e520ffd388bc3513db315ef5a51a2b3ac3d706","tid":1187624,"uid":120199,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T19:19:31.000Z","msg":"自慰得道"},{"pid":"ef5c1b4c641bac084221f6aa26d749a4d1c5c758","tid":1187624,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T19:22:37.000Z","msg":"jmny<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21bd079eef542c9ad3e643e1ad8803c1f55613be","tid":1187624,"uid":241471,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T19:23:21.000Z","msg":"樓主已經悟得大道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d410bd315c4a437fe5b059c22fe2831a909a2932","tid":1187624,"uid":209120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T19:25:17.000Z","msg":"自慰得多會越嚟越冇感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f69dd9d63f37b4a29c72e4bda6098004d85be3","tid":1187624,"uid":193476,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T19:31:31.000Z","msg":"樓主從自慰棒中悟得真理，實在係一個福份"},{"pid":"88a19fad7b8e274dd92fc70b53757c19714fe721","tid":1187624,"uid":213142,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T20:10:03.000Z","msg":"屌你睇到尾先知廣告"},{"pid":"9f2f9ecefeaaad738303fd661f80b7a9cce88a25","tid":1187624,"uid":10726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T20:12:17.000Z","msg":"我對肥仔有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f550b41c21a30d822a192451dde3973b09d8f2e9","tid":1187624,"uid":125742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T05:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9b7e81bb379d31befd63d6f9688b5c98c34b9d","tid":1187624,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T05:31:50.000Z","msg":"實戰救港<br />\n<br />\n[69兵法] 排陣+策略 *習近平權鬥*<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1187830\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1187830</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"974f67fbd2139d4d4b2fba1bbf9e79e4326c8802","tid":1187624,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco